ennet_dataset.Rd

ennet dataset retrieved as of 4 October 2020

ennet_dataset

Format

A tibble with 8650 rows and 10 columns

VariableDescription
themeThematic area
topicTitle of the question/topic
userName of ennet user either asking the question/topic or providing responses
userCodeCode for ennet user asking the question/topic or providing responses
jobJob title of ennet user asking the question/topic or providing responses
roleAssigned role of ennet user
date_timeDate and time a question/topic is raised or answer is provided
typeWhether a question or an answer
codeCode for the question/topic or answer
postThe question/topic raised or the answer provided

Source

https://www.en-net.org
